          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Aid to Homeowners with Crumbling Foundations Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development to provide grants&nbsp;for states to assist&nbsp;residential-building owners&nbsp;in repairing or replacing&nbsp;concrete foundations that have deteriorated due to pyrrhotite (an iron sulfide mineral).</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-25T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
